{"parse":{"title":"Raw Longjaw Mud Snapper","pageid":38446,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_32\n|name=Raw Longjaw Mud Snapper\n|level=5\n|quality=common\n|effect=Use: Restores 61 health over 18 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|charges=1\n|stack=20\n|sell={{cost|||1}}\n|ilvl=15\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Raw Longjaw Mud Snappers''' live in the murk and mud at the bottom of the water.\n==Source==\n'''Raw Longjaw Mud Snappers''' can be caught by [[fishing]] in the waters of [[Ashenvale]], [[Darnassus]], [[Darkshore]], [[Dun Morogh]], [[Elwynn Forest]], [[Hillsbrad Foothills]], [[Loch Modan]], [[Mulgore]], [[Redridge Mountains]], [[Stonetalon Mountains]], [[The Barrens]], [[Tirisfal Glades]], [[Westfall]], as well as the waters in the capital cities.\n\nThe required fishing skill for these fish is one, however the real requirement depends on the fishing location, since caught fish are not distinguished by skill level but by the body of water they reside in.  For example, in [[Mulgore]] Raw Longjaw Mud Snappers can be caught at any skill level, however in [[Ashenvale]] the ability to fish requires a skill level of 55 and thus the level requirement rises for that body of water.\n\n==Raw Longjaw Mud Snapper as an Ingredient==\n\n===Cooking===\n*[[Longjaw Mud Snapper]]\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6289}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_longjaw_mud_snapper.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]"}}}